{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing that has to be talked about is when it finally, when kids were finally over there-- and many of them were much older than 13-- eventually, the trucks came, loaded up the kids onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The trucks turned around and went into the directions of the smokestacks that we, that we saw spewing out the smoke, whose stench we smelled of burnt flesh already the moment we got out of the train.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even some white flakes would fall down on us from the ashes that would, like snow would fall on us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These-- then the kids were gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then the same thing went, anybody that needs medical attention over here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we need you to work and things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And people that went over there to the side and figured, yeah, they need us to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So maybe they mean what they say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Give us medical attention, and even if, if need be, a day or two rest before we send you to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some people believed in that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they went over now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "By that time, my brother and I had for a long time had recognized that the only way is to be, to be available to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't believe that they would give you any kind of rest or anything like that, although it sounded very, very tantalizing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so as people went over there that weren't in any worse shape than we were, in fact, everybody that was there really would have needed medical attention, if it comes right down to it, including ourselves.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we didn't go for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we knew that our only chance would be survival.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had heard already then, too, that the Nazis had really were thrown back in many places.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
